			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="PAD where a character who doesn't have the ointment applied steps into the shadowcurse and considers applying some. &#xD;&#xA;Only triggers if someone has spare ointment in their inventory. (At least one application)&#xD;&#xA;Plays only if 2 or more characters present: first to speak doesn't have the ointment applied on them. SH speaks first if she can.&#xD;&#xA;WRITER, don't forget to update the voicebark file SCL_ShadowCurse_VB_WantsOintment if you change the structure here!" />
